Lance Corporal Sunday Awolola, the soldier who allegedly raped a female student of Adekunle Ajasin University Akungba Akoko (AAUA) in Ondo state has been arraigned at a Magistrate's court sitting in Akure. Awolola is charged with an offence contrary to section 357 and punishable under section 358 of the criminal code cap 37 vol. Laws of the Ondo state of Nigeria.



